description: John Mattson Fastighetsföretagen AB owns and administrates residential and commercial properties. The company is headquartered in Lidingoe, Stockholm and currently employs 30 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2019-06-05. The company owns, manages and develops residential and commercial properties. The commercial premises complement the residential portfolio and primarily provide services to the residential tenants. The Company’s property portfolio mainly consists of residential property, more than 2170 rental apartments. The firm is active locally.
naicsNationalIndustry: Lessors of Residential Buildings and Dwellings
